item.title: CVE-2023-0498|2024-08-02T05:10:56.311Z -- unknown -- wp%20education
item.description: The WP Education WordPress plugin before 1.2.7 does not have CSRF check when activating plugins, which could allow attackers to make logged in admins activate arbitrary plugins present on the blog via a CSRF attack
